# Project docs are agent context

Before inventing enrollment, payments, Meta landing, or deploy behavior, read the matching doc under `docs/` (start at [docs/README.md](docs/README.md)).

| Area | Doc |
|------|-----|
| Enrollment wizard / APIs / application documents | `docs/enrollment/flows-and-entrypoints.md` |
| `/landing/*` Meta Ads (classic vs narrative) | `docs/landings-meta-ads.md` |
| Stripe | `docs/stripe-configuration.md` |
| Deploy / Brevo IP / email overrides | `docs/operational-runbook.md`, `docs/deployment-guide.md` |
